=== 车站装饰 ===
4号线车站装饰采用方形立柱的两面用马赛克小砖块拼贴成抽象的京剧脸谱图案<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2008-10/05/content_10149406.htm 北京地铁4号线装修方案确定] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2008-10/05/content_10149406.htm |date=20090524022104 }}，新华网，2008年10月05日。</ref>。

6号线车站装饰选用老北京传统的青砖、[[檩|檩条]]、[[砖雕|砖雕]]等元素，并设置有公共艺术作品《四季平安》<ref>{{Cite web|title=《四季平安》 {{!}} 北京地铁官方网站|url=https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/1.html|accessdate=2020-12-12|author=|date=|format=|work=www.bjsubway.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017141412/https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/1.html}}</ref>、《事事平安》<ref>{{Cite web|title=《事事平安》{{!}} 北京地铁官方网站|url=https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/2.html|accessdate=2020-12-12|author=|date=|format=|work=www.bjsubway.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017141407/https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/2.html}}</ref>和《玉堂富贵》<ref>{{Cite web|title=《玉堂富贵》 {{!}} 北京地铁官方网站|url=https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/3.html|accessdate=2020-12-12|author=|date=|format=|work=www.bjsubway.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017141407/https://www.bjsubway.com/station/xltwhq/line6/pal/3.html}}</ref>。

